### Test API cho enhanced promotion logic

### 1. Tạo AUTO promotion
POST http://localhost:8080/api/promotions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "promotionType": "auto",
    "discountType": "PERCENTAGE",
    "discountValue": 15,
    "minOrderValue": 100000,
    "startDate": "2025-09-01",
    "endDate": "2025-12-31",
    "usageLimit": null,
    "priority": 1,
    "status": "active"
}

### 2. Tạo COUPON promotion
POST http://localhost:8080/api/promotions
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "SAVE20",
    "promotionType": "coupon",
    "discountType": "PERCENTAGE", 
    "discountValue": 20,
    "minOrderValue": 50000,
    "startDate": "2025-09-01",
    "endDate": "2025-12-31",
    "usageLimit": 100,
    "priority": 2,
    "status": "active"
}

### 3. Tìm AUTO promotions active
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/auto-promotions?orderValue=150000

### 4. Tìm promotion tốt nhất cho user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/best-auto/1?orderValue=150000

### 5. Validate promotion với mã COUPON
POST http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/validate/1?promotionCode=SAVE20&orderValue=150000

### 6. Validate promotion không có mã (AUTO)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/validate/1?orderValue=150000

### 7. User claim COUPON promotion trước
POST http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/claim/1/SAVE20

### 8. Validate lại COUPON sau khi claim
POST http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/validate/1?promotionCode=SAVE20&orderValue=150000

### 9. Test với order value không đủ minimum
POST http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/validate/1?promotionCode=SAVE20&orderValue=30000

### 10. Test AUTO promotion với order value không đủ minimum
POST http://localhost:8080/api/promotions/validate/1?orderValue=50000
